<i>MichaÃ«l Lessard</i> - Ã‰tudiant B.C.L., LL. B. (Hons) Ã  la FacultÃ© de droit de lâ€™UniversitÃ© McGill";s:10:"post_title";s:29:"Lâ€™indignation. (Et aprÃ¨s?)";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:21:"lindignation-et-apres";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2014-12-02 08:35:18";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2014-12-02 13:35:18";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:37:"http://www.faitsetcauses.com/?p=12345";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"1";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:5:"12650";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2015-04-20 21:03:32";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2015-04-21 02:03:32";s:12:"post_content";s:5198:"<p style="text-align: justify;" align="center"><strong>Ã‰MILIE LE-HUY -Â Dans la dÃ©cision <a href="http://scc-csc.lexum.com/scc-csc/scc-csc/fr/item/15272/index.do?r=AAAAAQAOc2lkbmV5IGNoYXJsZXMB">R. c. Nur</a>, laÂ Cour suprÃªme du Canada a dÃ©clarÃ© invalides les peines minimales et obligatoires de trois (3) ans pour la premiÃ¨re infraction et de (5) cinq pour une rÃ©cidive concernant les infractions de possession dâ€™une arme Ã  feu prohibÃ©e. Voici un aperÃ§u de la dÃ©cision.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><a href="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Prison-TroisRivieres_PLD_20140524_046.1000.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-12480" style="width: 560px; height: 312px;" alt="Sans titre" src="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Prison-TroisRivieres_PLD_20140524_046.1000.jpg" width="1000" height="662" /></a></p>
